	(201,1,'2012-11-29 01:06:39','2012-11-29 01:06:39','<h2>ASIS International</h2>\r\nASIS International is the largest organization for security professionals, with over 37,000 members worldwide. Founded in 1955, ASIS is dedicated to increasing the effectiveness and productivity of security professionals. We provide educational programs and materials that address broad security topics, such as the ASIS Annual Seminar and Exhibits, and publishes Security Management, the industrys leading magazine. ASIS is an organization that represents the interests of the security management profession to businesses, the media, government entities, and the public.\r\n<h2>Orlando Chapter 063</h2>\r\nJoining ASIS International also allows members in Central Florida to participate on the local level by joining our ASIS Orlando Chapter. Established on July 22, 1969, we have a long history of security professionals who have made a great impact locally and nationally on our industry.','About','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-8','','','2012-11-29 01:06:39','2012-11-29 01:06:39','',2,'http://127.0.0.1/ASIS_Orlando/wordpress/?p=201',0,'revision','',0),
